snippet.textDisplay:
Julie Lyrics

Julie wants money
Julie wants fame
She knows the tricks
She knows the game x (2)

Hey Julie main tumse pyar karta tha
Tera aitbar karta tha
Haan tujhpe dil se marta tha
Tu meri raat ki shehzadiyon si
Apsara thi, dil nasheen thi
Jaane kyun mere dil ko toone yun toda

Ho Julie lagti mujhko tu bhole si
Haan mujhse tu yeh boli thi
Kisi ki aur na hogi
Tu mujhko thaam kar mera sath degi
Gir gaya to hath degi
Oh farebi yeh jhooth toone kyun bola

Ho baaton mein teri, baaton mein
Aaya teri baaton mein main deewana
Raaton mein sooni raaton mein
Tanha tanha raaton mein
Mujhe chhod ke chali gayi kahan
Ho ik musafir tha main tanha
Le liya ishq ka yeh panga
Teri dhokhebaaz aakhon mein
Aake maine yeh jahan chhoda oh Julie

Rahegi mere bin ab tu
Chalega mera yeh jaadu
Miloonga tujhko main har su
Kabhi awaaz meri sunke padpe
Khushbu meri tere ghar pe
Tujhko sone degi na jeene degi Julie

Ho daulat kamana hai izzat kamana
Ek din duniya se saabko hai jaana
Pyar hi mahan hai baaki sab saaman hai
Aane wali naslon ko mera yeh paigam hai
Ke paisa jawani nahi rehte oh jaani
Inpe bharosa nahi
Rishte aur naate aur pyar wali baatein
Inmein hai yeh zindagi

Tu bhookh bharke, yun akad ke
Kare ya to kya dikhana chahati
Ya ke toone kaise rang badal ke
Dheeme halke se dekho aaj ke kya kar diya Julie

Gorakh kaisa yeh dhanda hai
Jahan har koyi nanga hai
Nikla jannat se banda hai
Nahi jisko sharam kyun ho karam
Jab aasman chhuye bharam
Insan ko dekho kis gali laake chhoda

O aa Julie
O meri Julie
O Julie..

Julie wants money
Do you want some money?
Julie wants fame
And she can do a little bit of fame too
She knows the tricks
She knows all the tricks, yes knows it baby
She knows the game
Julie knows the game, like that!



Thank me later
